    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain sends power through a variable M-differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis maintains excellent lateral rigidity, with suspension geometry optimized for communicative feedback. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity matches the high-output performance. This driver-focused machine offers a visceral analog experience with the mechanical sound profile only individual throttle bodies can provide.",
      "price": 34500.0,
